Usage: BIND <key> SHRINK_WINDOW
  This function decreases the size of the current window by one row.

See Also: 
  BIND GROW_WINDOW
  BIND HIDE_WINDOW
  BIND LIST_WINDOWS
  BIND KILL_WINDOW
  BIND NEW_WINDOW
